          Tian Lu, Feiwu Chen, J. Comput. Chem., 33, 580-592 (2012)
          Tian Lu, J. Chem. Phys., 161, 082503 (2024)
 See "How to cite Multiwfn.pdf" in Multiwfn binary package for more information

